Learning_Imported_ContentObject.description: Display information used to describe an instance of an object. This 'optional' information is for outbound descriptive purposes only and is not processed on inbound Workday Web Services requests.

Learning_Imported_ContentObjectID.description: The unique identifier type. Each "ID" for an instance of an object contains a type and a value. A single instance of an object can have multiple "ID" but only a single "ID" per "type".  Some "types" require a reference to a parent instance.

Learning_Imported_ContentObject.description: Contains a unique identifier for an instance of an object.

description: Identifies imported contents using unique references for updates. Leave blank when creating imported content.

Learning_Imported_Content_Data.description: Reference ID for the imported content.
Unique title for the imported content.

description: Contains data for the imported content, i.e. name, description, version, & ID.
